# Final Outcome

After completing these steps, the solution will support an event-driven architecture where incoming requests are queued, processed asynchronously, stored in Cosmos DB, and enriched through external AI services before being returned to end users. This design improves scalability, reliability, and separation of responsibilities across application components.
